   "code": "VMBS-ABM-Skimming- 2024 - ABM Skimming 2024",
   "pid": 398,
   "exc": "Replace Magnetic Stripe Cards",
   "rec": "Replace Magnetic Stripe Cards",
   "find": "The primary ABM card used by VMBS is the magnetic stripe card, which is inherently easier to clone, providing fraudsters with opportunities to exploit the society's members. It is important to note that even after implementing the SSS toolkit, VMBS continues to experience elevated levels of fraud. This may be due to other financial institutions not adopting the same technology, as their customers' cards are not exposed to the same risks due to the use of EMV technology. Debit Card FraudJan-23Feb-23Mar-23Apr-23May-23Jun-23Jul-23Aug-23Sep-23Oct-23Nov-23Dec-23 N/A 129,000 574,000 150,000 - 29,500",
